text: The Central Park Squirrel Census is a scientific survey to try to determine the amount of squirrels in Central Park. Based on the 2019 census, there were 2,373 Eastern Gray squirrels in Central Park. The survey has been covered by various media. ==References== ==External links== * Link to census Category:Biological censuses Category:Censuses in the United States Category:Central Park Category:2019 in New York City Category:Squirrels in human culture
